e8feb65b7a8081b1f446b9c9c895f","tid":193144,"uid":53535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實洗機洗得多會唔會愈黎愈lag<br />\nGoogle 完有啲話會有啲會唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋想問<br />\n1.洗機洗得最徹底嘅方法係用洗機碟定電腦內置個還原原廠?<br />\n<br />\n2.洗得多會唔會有問題?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n還原原廠個人認為好垃圾, 但對於唔識down返drive同裝window既人係唯一選擇<br />\n要徹底一定係格式化os個hd再裝window<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n唔會<br />\n洗得多而lag多數係硬件開始老化<br />\n例如hd收收地皮就會lag<br />\n或者可能係你隻眼快左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前裝 visual studio 個陣裝極都裝唔到，還原左幾次，之後好似有啲lag<br />\n買左半年左右咋，唔會咁快老化掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e144e6d8697ac71757aeabf003870628041535","tid":193144,"uid":31707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"洗機通常要用清水加眼鏡布，濕水輕力抹就ok!"},{"pid":"1d5ea00b249d78414f6f3084992cf6a7ca7f43fc","tid":193144,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"屌 真係有人答呢啲智障問題<br />\n<br />\non9小學雞樓主"},{"pid":"6a6b38bd12383b414543f1a2238aebc0a3af606d","tid":193144,"uid":48491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.洗機洗得最徹底嘅方法係用洗機碟定電腦內置個還原原廠?</blockquote><br />\n最徹底緊係低階格式化啦仲問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>2.洗得多會唔會有問題?</blockquote><br />\n點為之多？如果你隻硬碟讀寫無限次實有問題㗎"}]}